svg.title: System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US10 - Assign train to route

g.text: System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US10 - Assign train to route
select train (assuming there is at least 1 train available)
returns message error and continues to show the list
loads existing stations and possible cargo
list available stations (US7) and request for station selection
select start station (assuming there are at least 2 stations)
request which cargo should be picked up
select cargo for the respective station
[While the player hasn't finished the selection operation]
lists the remaining stations and request to select a station
[There is a railway line between the last 2 selected stations]
request which cargo should be picked up
select cargo for the respective station
continues to show the list and request a new station
save the route with selected train, stations, and cargo
